{"tid":2347983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"懲教署將斥資逾1億元 於小欖裝設人臉辨識電子鎖","createTime":"2020-12-31T11:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T18:57:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ee087e0ae9a0581696861b0318567c17054fef96","tid":2347983,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"懲教署將斥資逾1億元，在小欖精神病治療中心設置電鎖保安系統，取代現時的手動系統。新電鎖系統將配備人臉辨識功能，以確認懲教署職員身份。懲教署指，新系統可提升監獄管理的效率及保安水平，但因小欖精神病治療中心須翻新或改建部份設施方能安裝新系統，加上工程期間中心須如常運作，工程時間料長達6年，預計新系統於2027年12月啟用。<br />\n<br />\n保安局和懲教署向立法會提交的文件指，計劃在小欖精神病治療中心裝置電鎖保安系統，取代舊式的手動系統。文件指，新系統為電動機械鎖開關系統，配合閉路電視、人臉辨識功能、對講機及召喚按鈕運作。當有懲教人員按召喚按鈕要求開啟閘門時，閉路電視的人臉辨識功能會確認懲教署職員身份，訊號將傳送到控制室，由控制室職員核實職員身份，方開啟閘門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/TD3VJ5ASBBBFJHVVWGVVZUENTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FTD3VJ5ASBBBFJHVVWGVVZUENTY%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=d135da84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201231%2FTD3VJ5ASBBBFJHVVWGVVZUENTY%2F&h=984d5ce0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201231/TD3VJ5ASBBBFJHVVWGVVZUENTY/</a>"},{"pid":"80ead3bffda4a746845136be8ec2eee8609d0523","tid":2347983,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:55:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d393fad5aea3d3e275d6ddedb5e85eb253d289","tid":2347983,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42213aff5c9338e841e7f2b46307fd42